GulfTalent.com
HR Coordinator
Charterhouse
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 4 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Charterhouse is working with an innovative and dynamic digital marketing agency based in Dubai. They are currently experiencing a period of growth and are looking to hire a HR Coordinator to join their business. Reporting into the HR Manager you will be responsible for recruitment, on boarding, employee relations and HR administration within the busy office.
REQUIREMENTS
The successful candidate should hold a Degree within Human Resource Management or a related subject.
You should have more than two years experience working within an agency environment, ideally working with clients in the digital marketing and media industries. This role is high pressured and demanding, it will require you to work on multiple positions at one time therefore exceptional time management is crucial. You will also be responsible for administration within HR so exceptional organisational skills are essential in order to prioritise and manage a heavy workload.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
During the last ten years, Charterhouse has been operating across Dubai, Abu Dhabi and the GCC Markets. In many ways, we were the recruiter who established and set the standards within the regional recruitment industry benchmarking and innovating the service levels associated to Search and Selection.
Charterhouse understands the dynamics attached to talent acquisition, relationship management and the required service levels within the regional industry. Our heritage is now our main strength as we continue to work within our core markets to deliver key account management and strong contingency recruitment practices to our clients and candidates.
